nextPage.description: If there is another page of results, the URL of the next page.

maxResults.description: The maximum number of items that could be returned.

startAt.description: The index of the first item returned.

isLast.description: Whether this is the last page.

key.description: This property is no longer available and will be removed from the documentation soon. See the [deprecation notice](https://developer.atlassian.com/cloud/jira/platform/deprecation-notice-user-privacy-api-migration-guide/) for details.

accountId.description: The account ID of the user, which uniquely identifies the user across all Atlassian products. For example, *5b10ac8d82e05b22cc7d4ef5*. Returns *unknown* if the record is deleted and corrupted, for example, as the result of a server import.
